title: Black Eyed Peas Collection
description:
This torrent contains all 6 Black Eyed Peas albums plus a rare a Capella album. It also contains a large collection of remix versions of BEP songs (including versions from Full Tilt and Ultimix) - plus several solo tracks and collaborations from BEP members Will I Am and Fergie.

The albums and some of the remixes were all ripped by me from CD. Many of the remixes were recorded from vinyl by me on a Numark TTX turntable with an Ortofon Arkiv stylus using Adobe Audition software.

All tracks are 320k bitrate apart from a small number of the remixes that I got off other people.

All files are tagged including cover art.
